<C>__{val}
<D>__{earl, get real. what does she need with a guy like me?}
<A>__{earl is dumbfounded.}
<C>__{earl}
<D>__{what was that? all this time she's not good enough for you. now, suddenly, you're not good enough for her? god, my work is never done. you don't decide is you're worthless, she does. but you gotta give her a chance!}
<A>__{val lowers the jack letting the truck down.}
